		<div>Ok, I only skimmed the thread but I'll throw in my 2 cents, and as a bonus I'll give the devs an idea of where I am and my guild's progression in an attempt to give them a better idea of where I am coming from.<br />
Level: 70<br />
AA: ~400<br />
Guild Progression: Working through CoA named but have not gotten to MataMuram yet, Killed Yar'Lir, can clear all of Tacvi<br />
<br />
1.  I want an upgrade to Improved Invis.  Self target only, an AA that can match the apilities of Rogue's Shroud of Stealth.  Short reuse timer say 15 mins.  Could also make it snare ME for balance.  Make it long duration too say 10 minutes.<br />
<br />
2. I like the idea of a MGB type AA that lets me TL an entire raid to any TL spell I have.  Could even make it take the same number of portal stones as the number of people in range.  Would provide some kind of limitation to it.<br />
<br />
3. I want a MUCH upgraded Mind Crash.  Shorter reuse timer, more agro reduction, even faster cast time.<br />
<br />
4. Along the same lines I would like to see an AA (with a long reuse timer say 72 mins) that lets me &quot;mega&quot; Mind Crash a mob and remove ALL agro it has on me.  So if I get agro running somewhere I have the option of rooting/snaring it and wiping me off it's agro list totally.  This would obviously help in a raid, maybe too much, so you could limit it to only work on a mob that has NOT been damaged by anyone.<br />
<br />
5.  Ability to take a group to my Secondary bind point like Teleport Bind to primary bind point.</div>
